ls good to the soul, if the movement makes you feel a certain way, that’s the class you want to show up in,” says Kevin Malone, a dance teacher and choreographer. Kevin is a black man with closely cropped hair wearing rectangular glasses. " loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;div id="resg-s1-38886" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 2000;         --source-height: 2500;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2000x2500+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3b%2F32%2F4e07f4b64d13960f92b9faca4504%2F10-min.png 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2000x2500+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3b%2F32%2F4e07f4b64d13960f92b9faca4504%2F10-min.png 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2000x2500+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3b%2F32%2F4e07f4b64d13960f92b9faca4504%2F10-min.png 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2000x2500+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3b%2F32%2F4e07f4b64d13960f92b9faca4504%2F10-min.png 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2000x2500+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3b%2F32%2F4e07f4b64d13960f92b9faca4504%2F10-min.png 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2000x2500+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/web